{"tid":1319292,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我地有冇整到一個資料庫","createTime":"2019-07-15T06:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T07:36:56.000Z","uid":207614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d7a7733547b6e9c52b475e348a6c38cd4cb45c6c","tid":1319292,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:30:27.000Z","msg":"由6月9號到而家咁多大大小小既衝突<br />\n文宣組似乎每一次都係要係一大堆突發po入面汁返D證據出黎<br />\n我地其實有冇一個整合到一個資料庫<br />\n分好日子分好時序各樣野<br />\n好似懶人包咁可以一次過睇哂邊一日發生過咩事<br />\n一黎資訊太多需要整合(洗版洗到有D重要野容易miss out)<br />\n二黎容易清算<br />\n<br />\n新資訊好容易吞走舊資訊<br />\n我唔想大家忘記左烈士既犧牲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=etlBZInTE-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DetlBZInTE-I&d=Nl%2Bce6%2FxXxAB2W4e8qnvdrJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=61f75a13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=etlBZInTE-I</a>"},{"pid":"cbf2093c9509503ea1fc3d9b6c36a2b19bbc0d96","tid":1319292,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:36:56.000Z","msg":"推一推"}]}